5.title: TUFLOW CATCH Changelog
5.content: New releases are typically linked to the release of major new features and/or improvements in the computational hydraulic engines. Whilst some changes in results can be expected between releases due to computational engine improvements, the intent is not to have any changes in results between minor releases.
